				<div class="hvres-meaning"><a href="/whv/𧰝"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x27C1D;</span></a><a href="/whv/𡤜"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x2191C;</span></a><a href="/whv/𡤵"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x21935;</span></a><a href="/whv/𧹌"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x27E4C;</span></a><p class="gray small" style="padding-left:10px"><a href="/fonts.php">Không hiện chữ?</a></p></div><p class="hvres-source">Một số bài thơ có sử dụng</p>
				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-H%C3%A1n-Si%C3%AAu/B%E1%BA%A1ch-%C4%90%E1%BA%B1ng-giang-ph%C3%BA/poem-vkX_Mo8oekmvcSW48K_TFg">Bạch Đằng giang phú - 白藤江賦</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-H%C3%A1n-Si%C3%AAu/author-8OezdZDSC-q-9wfu_BOuVw">Trương Hán Siêu</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%A2n-Nh%C3%A2n-Trung/%C4%90%E1%BA%A1i-B%E1%BA%A3o-tam-ni%C3%AAn-Nh%C3%A2m-Tu%E1%BA%A5t-khoa-ti%E1%BA%BFn-s%C4%A9-%C4%91%E1%BB%81-danh-k%C3%BD/poem-lmPI_Y7GazogxyWzI82qMg">Đại Bảo tam niên Nhâm Tuất khoa tiến sĩ đề danh ký - 大寶弎年壬戌科進士題名記</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%A2n-Nh%C3%A2n-Trung/author-eOFIe3QgfrDzlduYauxtuQ">Thân Nhân Trung</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-B%E1%BB%99t/%C4%90%E1%BA%B1ng-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-c%C3%A1c-t%E1%BB%B1/poem-FT3LNnXR5KVN9HD70_hBOw">Đằng Vương các tự - 滕王閣序</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-B%E1%BB%99t/author-_ZqxSvkbsUwNbnMEINI85Q">Vương Bột</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Khuy%E1%BA%BFt-danh-Vi%E1%BB%87t-Nam/%C4%90%E1%BB%95ng-H%E1%BB%93-b%C3%BAt-ph%C3%BA/poem-zjv_6tPCykW3dsLfeEVU1g">Đổng Hồ bút phú - 董狐筆賦</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Khuy%E1%BA%BFt-danh-Vi%E1%BB%87t-Nam/author-kBTBt5Mbi6PPrH2sJkQAPw">Khuyết danh Việt Nam</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Nh%C3%A2n-T%C3%B4ng/L%C3%A2m-chung-di-chi%E1%BA%BFu/poem-I86uGQtK3uDAayDqWSRvWw">Lâm chung di chiếu - 臨終遺詔</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Nh%C3%A2n-T%C3%B4ng/author-sMXrZTDvW5uflSvv6NTMXQ">Lý Nhân Tông</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4-Th%E1%BB%A9c/Ph%C3%B3ng-H%E1%BA%A1c-%C4%91%C3%ACnh-k%C3%BD/poem-G9cZsg_CWtgdk2ilh8g8AQ">Phóng Hạc đình ký - 放鶴亭記</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4-Th%E1%BB%A9c/author-ZsPeAEZWTH-jxxg2cYfLgg">Tô Thức</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.th